      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation with solid value for the right buyer. It shows age and wear consistent with its condition, but it remains a practical option for someone seeking low-cost mobility, a project car, or a straightforward work-and-commuter vehicle. Priced to move and represented with transparency.",
