      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer who wants dependable basic transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates a practical purchase with plenty of life left for everyday use, light commuting, or a project-minded owner. A sensible opportunity to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
