      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life and potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and can still be a great fit for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a solid project to tinker with. I\u2019m the kind of seller who likes to be upfront, so if you want a budget-friendly car without the sales fluff, this one is worth a look. Priced fairly for what it is, and a great chance to get on the road without spending a fortune.",
